overview: >-
  The user initiated a request for a complete aesthetic overhaul of their sleep
  questionnaire app, aiming for a more polished and appealing design. The agent
  began by conducting a thorough review of the existing styling, identifying
  areas for improvement in color, typography, spacing, form elements, and
  overall visual interest.

  The approach involved implementing a new sleep-themed color palette,
  redesigning the main form layout with subtle background elements and an
  enhanced progress indicator, and revamping the welcome screen with feature
  cards. Individual UI components like checkboxes, radio buttons, and sliders
  were also polished for a more modern feel. A key decision was to apply
  consistent styling across all questionnaire sections, replacing generic gray
  boxes with themed card-like groupings.

  During the process, a console error related to  values in input fields
  was identified and fixed by safely converting  to an empty string. User
  feedback, including a screenshot, highlighted inconsistencies in the Report
  section's card header colors, which were subsequently unified to a single
  sleep-themed gradient. All hardcoded gray and blue text colors were replaced
  with theme variables, and section border opacity was increased for better
  definition. The outcome is a visually cohesive, calming, and professional
  sleep questionnaire app.
